		<s:RichEditableText id="myRET1" width="100%">
			<s:p>The Epsitech Electronic Performance Management Suite (ePMS) empowers government organisations with the latest available online tools to focus on and fine-tune the discipline of organisational and individual Performance management (PM).</s:p>
			<s:list listStyleType="diamond" >
				<s:li>ePMS has been developed in line with the Government Wide Framework for Monitoring and evaluation as well as other relevant legislation such as the PFMA and MFMA.</s:li>
				<s:li>ePMS can be offered as an “end to end solution” consisting of online (web enabled), electronic Suite of tools as well as implementation methodologies.</s:li>
				<s:li>ePMS enables organisations to capture and track all activities related to individual and organisational performance with a view to ensuring that these activities are correctly aligned to organisational as well as provincial and national government strategy and goals.</s:li>
